snippet.title: Feral Flowers [Trailer]
snippet.description:
Feral Flowers is a quick-fire roguelite platformer. If you like indie gaming tropes and hate hay fever, you should play it:

https://starriver.itch.io/feral
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1763060/Feral_Flowers/
